\item \strong{Build} spatial line segments between consecutive root nodes
\item \strong{Calculate} geometric metrics: 3D length, azimuth, inclination, slope
\item \strong{Join} root segments with tree stem locations
\item \strong{Aggregate} metrics at root and tree level (lengths, depth, orientations)
\item \strong{Build} 2D convex hull polygons representing root system spread
\item \strong{Estimate} 3D bounding volume of root systems
\item \strong{Analyze} inter-tree root overlap competition
\item \strong{Compute} root-to-trunk distances
